# Zoom Blocks

## Zoom Blocks

Zoom Blocks are a useful tool to increase the readability of code in Snap. To access the Zoom Blocks feature, simply go up to **Settings** in the upper left, and select the second option in the list, **Zoom Blocks**. 

![](../.gitbook/assets/zoomblocksetting%20%281%29.png)

Once selected, an interface pops up which allows you to increase the zoom on your code and shows you a preview.

![Use slider to Zoom Blocks ](data:image/png;base64,)
